														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2268718">
									

<p>I'm really, <em>really</em> enjoying your Antimemetics stories, qntm. They really do a good job of showing how quickly horrible, frightening, and confusing it would be to have something eat up your memories, something that the average person thinks is untouchable.</p>
<p>+1 for the awesome story.</p>
<p>I'd give another +1 if that would inspire you to write more.</p>
<p>And, I'll give you a permanent +1 for everything ever, if you end up one day <em>deleting</em> all these tales and claiming you never wrote them :D</p>

							</div>

								
					
