<p>Thanks for your positive thoughts, I was very uncertain about posting this one. I have some more ideas for Tales in this area, so stay tuned.</p>
<p>On a semi-serious note: the number one ground rule in the Antimemetics division is that you <em>do not</em> pretend to have forgotten about something. Either you remember, and you say you remember, or you forget, and you say you forgot. Memory is too serious to play games with. ;)</p>

